						<div class="postbody">ADC and SBC touch all flags NVZC.
<br />
<br />Pretty much all NES games (except for a few obscure ones that almost nobody in my country probably has) use the NMI to detect the start of <span class="posthilit">vertical</span> blanking.
<br />
<br />What would SEV be needed for?
<br />
<br />BIT immediate does not exist on the original 6502.</div>

